{"title":"AHHA! Is the Toaster the World’s Simplest, Most Portable Bike Rack?","link":"https://bikerumor.com/ahha-toaster-simple-portable-bike-rack/","date":1696939200000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-hero.jpeg\" alt=\"AHHA Toaster Bike Rack hero\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-hero.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-hero-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-hero-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-hero-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-hero-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-hero-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Hailing from Atlanta, Georgia comes a new <a href=\"https://ahha.bike/\">cycling equipment company</a> by the name of AHHA Inc and they bring the news of their <a href=\"https://ahha.bike/products/toaster\">new bike rack</a>, the Toaster, which they are claiming to be the simplest, most portable bike rack in the world. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-new-rack-goofin.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-new-rack-goofin-800x534.jpeg\" alt=\"AHHA Toaster Bike Rack new rack goofin'\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-new-rack-goofin-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-new-rack-goofin-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-new-rack-goofin-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-new-rack-goofin-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-new-rack-goofin-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-new-rack-goofin.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo c. AHHA Inc.New Rack Goofin’</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Toaster helps solve both temporary and permanent bike parking. It can hold one to five bikes of all disciplines, from skinny road tires, to the fatter tires of some downhill rigs, and everything in between. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This new, portable rack is made from recycled aluminum and can fold down completely flat, and only “weighs as much as a cat”. Also, the rack is powder coated to help keep it’s appearance fresh in both weather and during the rigors of traveling.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-folded-flat.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-folded-flat-800x422.jpeg\" alt=\"AHHA Toaster Bike Rack folded flat\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-folded-flat-800x422.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-folded-flat-297x157.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-folded-flat-120x63.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-folded-flat-768x405.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-folded-flat.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-staight-on.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-staight-on-800x422.jpeg\" alt=\"AHHA Toaster Bike Rack staight on\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-staight-on-800x422.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-staight-on-297x157.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-staight-on-120x63.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-staight-on-768x405.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-staight-on.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-straight-down.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-straight-down-800x422.jpeg\" alt=\"AHHA Toaster Bike Rack new rack goofin'\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-straight-down-800x422.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-straight-down-297x157.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-straight-down-120x63.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-straight-down-768x405.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-straight-down.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-side-shot.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-side-shot-800x422.jpeg\" alt=\"AHHA Toaster Bike Rack side shot\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-side-shot-800x422.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-side-shot-297x157.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-side-shot-120x63.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-side-shot-768x405.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-side-shot.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Toaster can be stowed in car trunks, truck beds, or other similar small-to-medium spaces. AHHA says it’s constructed with quality materials and should “last a lifetime”. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-inserts-white-e1696355125736.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"245\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-inserts-white-e1696355125736-800x245.jpeg\" alt=\"AHHA Toaster Bike Rack inserts blue\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-inserts-white-e1696355125736-800x245.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-inserts-white-e1696355125736-297x91.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-inserts-white-e1696355125736-120x37.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-inserts-white-e1696355125736-768x235.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-inserts-white-e1696355125736.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Big Sky</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-inserts-pink-e1696355110977.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"248\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-inserts-pink-e1696355110977-800x248.jpeg\" alt=\"AHHA Toaster Bike Rack inserts pink\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-inserts-pink-e1696355110977-800x248.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-inserts-pink-e1696355110977-297x92.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-inserts-pink-e1696355110977-120x37.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-inserts-pink-e1696355110977-768x238.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-inserts-pink-e1696355110977.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Giro Pink</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>There are color-coded insert Grommets that are available to be installed into the slots to accommodate different tires sizes. Big Sky reduces the slot size to 51mm for gravel tires, and the Giro Pink reduces the slot down to 34mm for road tires. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Toaster works without the grommets as well, it just depends on how snug you want the bike to fit in the rack. And to note: no grommet is needed for mountain bike tires. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-having-beers.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-having-beers-800x534.jpeg\" alt=\"AHHA Toaster Bike Rack having beers\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-having-beers-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-having-beers-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-having-beers-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-having-beers-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-having-beers-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-having-beers.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Darren Kornas, Founder of AHHA says, “<em>As an active, multi-discipline rider myself, it seemed every event and every ride gathering featured bikes scattered about, leaning on whatever. More importantly, bikes were getting backed over by cars, damaged by falling over, and more. </em></p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Even at home the bikes are tough to manage between my bikes, the kids bikes, visiting friends, etc. I don’t like leaving my bikes on the ground, or precariously propped against the nearest stationary object. Toaster came to me in the middle of the night. I got up, and made my first sketch”. </em></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-the-office.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-the-office-800x534.jpeg\" alt=\"AHHA Toaster Bike Rack in the office\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-the-office-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-the-office-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-the-office-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-the-office-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-the-office-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-the-office.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Toaster Retail and Colors</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-Classic-Black.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"770\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-Classic-Black.jpeg\" alt=\"AHHA Toaster Bike Rack in Classic Black\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-Classic-Black.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-Classic-Black-297x286.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-Classic-Black-120x116.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-Classic-Black-768x739.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Classic Black (with the different sized grommets inserted)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-Full-Send.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"770\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-Full-Send.jpeg\" alt=\"AHHA Toaster Bike Rack in Full Send\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-Full-Send.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-Full-Send-297x286.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-Full-Send-120x116.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-Full-Send-768x739.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Full Send</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-Bleach.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"770\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-Bleach.jpeg\" alt=\"AHHA Toaster Bike Rack in Bleach\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-Bleach.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-Bleach-297x286.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-Bleach-120x116.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/AHHA-Toaster-Bike-Rack-in-Bleach-768x739.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Bleached</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Toaster is available for pre-order on their site now and retails for $429. It comes is three colors, Classic Black, Full Send (red), and Bleached (white)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Grommets inserts retail for $45.00 and come in Big Sky (light blue), and Giro Pink. <em> Giro Pink reduces wheel slot width to 34mm (road tires), and Big Sky reduces the wheels slot width to 51mm (gravel tires). No Grommet needed for MTB tires.</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"http://ahha.bike\">AHHA.Bike</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/ahha-toaster-simple-portable-bike-rack/\">AHHA! Is the Toaster the World’s Simplest, Most Portable Bike Rack?</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"e847a2ecc9df76b19e0a966755a26b612993bd737af67436ac2ba288a9cae441","category":"Cycling"}